Title: Colin Higgins Papers, ca. 1960-1987
Summary: Personal and professional correspondence, screenplays in various drafts, research materials, production reports, army and college notes, and photographs.
Description.abstract: Colin Higgins (1941-1988) was a screenwriter and director of the film comedies Harold and Maude, Silver streak, Foul Play, and Nine to Five. The collection consists of personal and professional correspondence, screenplays in various drafts, research materials, production reports, army and college notes, and photographs.
